Follow all project standards in [CLAUDE.md](mdc:CLAUDE.md) and every document it links to under `docs/` (`BEST-PRACTICES.md`, `BEST-PRACTICES-POSTGRESQL.md`, `CICD.md`, `DECISIONS.md`, `FAQ.md`). These are the same team-wide rules shared via `AGENTS.md` — this file just makes Cursor load them on every request.

Working agreement (also in CLAUDE.md):

- Before completing a task, run `npm run typecheck`, `npm run lint`, and the relevant tests — all must pass.
- Add or update tests for any new or changed logic.
- Never commit or push without explicit approval; if on `main`, branch first.
- Ask before destructive or outward-facing actions.
